### Comparison: k6 vs Artillery

| Feature | k6 | Artillery |
|---------|-----|-----------|
| **Scripting** | JavaScript (ES6) | YAML + optional JS |
| **Performance** | Very high (Go runtime) | Moderate (Node.js) |
| **Distributed Testing** | k6 Cloud | Artillery Pro |
| **Learning Curve** | Moderate | Low (declarative) |
| **Built‑in Checks** | Yes | Yes |
| **HTML Reports** | Via cloud/plugins | Built‑in |
| **WebSocket Testing** | Yes | Yes |

